    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture, style, and nationality of Haiti, a country in the Caribbean Sea that includes the western third of the island of Hispaniola and several smaller islands. The population is largely descended from enslaved Africans; the country won independence from France in 1804.</Note_Text>
